除非佢走資大陸佬個仔"},{"pid":"7f18ca842851af98712b1ca6ddc85293a20f1872","tid":285982,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"學佛<br />\n夠你學一世"},{"pid":"d9d839cce76a9fc714f16bc3730fb7fc93933c64","tid":285982,"uid":80529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"Same here 22歲 剛畢業<br />\n學科所限行頭窄，自問成績唔差，但揾到嘅工仲低過High Dip畢業。呢排無乜心機，旅行又去完<br />\n諗緊究竟揾一份咩工好。。。"},{"pid":"03db6dff7d4ac4560c4a7755d4b57990d59c0edd","tid":285982,"uid":621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"日日都唔知做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59ac5f68c98cc60b921de22c5f1ddc27d89c49c","tid":285982,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"我都想做廢青"},{"pid":"cc05e86c8624480d77c2d9c8d5e027d10cd0723e","tid":285982,"uid":67306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"屋企有冇錢 個樣靚唔靚仔冇得改變<br />\n但人生係自己決定的<br />\n<br />\n你覺得自己好廢既 冷靜一下 諗下自己想做咩<br />\n諗到就去做<br />\n想學車 上網申請 想讀書 睇下有冇邊間肯收你<br />\n想去旅行咪去囉<br />\n呢d先係人生<br />\n唔好再花時間諗點解自己咁廢 花多d時間諗下自己有咩想做 再去做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：25歲 OT中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9728ac1bf3c2fdbc66f69ced73b40cef4a06fa","tid":285982,"uid":52947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"19歲有類似感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家學下投資保障下自己將來"},{"pid":"1b1e7685eb65bdb87cae117d1de41c1952fd9f38","tid":285982,"uid":34158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:07:43.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身邊未經歷過呢d人生既人根本唔會明<br />\n只會叫你搵下興趣搵鍾意既野讀下<br />\n覺得你只係未想返工住<br />\n但你自己知自己冇目標冇興趣呢個世界上冇咩想要<br />\n突然覺得係自己身邊好耐一直相安無事既女朋友係重擔<br />\n諗都冇諗掉低左人<br />\n自己好渴望自己可以積極搵目標做人<br />\n但內心根本咩都唔想要個種感覺真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847927801550deccd677e98deb4cfac30907871b","tid":285982,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"三字頭都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4107b212b3a23bbd2efec68ace1ee55277d7cd09","tid":285982,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"22就23<br />\n今年grad <br />\n唔想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e099082e2696fc7774f41ecbdbccd1b7ba542152","tid":285982,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"大過你，又係讀書唔成<br />\n不過都叫有一門手藝<br />\n依家搵返自己興趣果一行嘅工，應該會好辛苦但係先碼做返自己擅長嘅野<br />\n<br />\n做散工真係唔好受，可有可無隨時俾人取代<br />\n而且得，一係讀到書岀黎搵零用錢，一係做散工做到幾廿歲都係一pet爛泥，好驚自己變成第二種<br />\n<br />\n如果你係絲，有身材正常樣又唔同講法<br />\n好多散工請靚女勁好pay又hae,返工下去下旅行真心好過返長工<br />\n<br />\n如果你係柒絲，又或者係巴，都係搵返份長工啦，香港係咁現實"},{"pid":"3cf66d2bf6504c65719265034e441a460f07fc83","tid":285982,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過得依種生活嘅屋企都有番咁上下啦吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企曾經試過窮到問人借錢<br />\n嗰刻開始我話我發唔到達都唔要再咁問人</blockquote><br />\n年輕人，廿二歲玩下啦<br />\n諗下平時有咩會令到你放鬆或者開心<br />\n打機又好，去下旅行都好<br />\n總之搵野玩<br />\n玩玩下你就知要返工搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  黎緊9月會去旅行 <br />\n純粹搬左去村屋 好似與世隔絕咁 交通又唔方便 又無電腦 無wifi 同老母，工人 相依為命 老豆翻工 所以先想學車 起碼有得周圍去</blockquote><br />\n我都係村屋撚，join個無限plan啦"},{"pid":"88d8030953f44e75b625bc4cb145157e618abd4d","tid":285982,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:16:04.000Z","msg":"27歲 做左份工 7年 一無是處 最近老闆減人工 想走但又無其他技能 唉"},{"pid":"2768929796480b62655c7df42ab1ec9a52d46174","tid":285982,"uid":66952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過得依種生活嘅屋企都有番咁上下啦吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企曾經試過窮到問人借錢<br />\n嗰刻開始我話我發唔到達都唔要再咁問人</blockquote><br />\n年輕人，廿二歲玩下啦<br />\n諗下平時有咩會令到你放鬆或者開心<br />\n打機又好，去下旅行都好<br />\n總之搵野玩<br />\n玩玩下你就知要返工搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你話想學車？爲咩？<br />\n為左搵工？搵份咩野工？<br />\n定為左買車玩？？<br />\n&hellip;依啲咪目標囉<br />\n成年人，唔洗人地搵目標比你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉分身轉唔切？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4ed6d134a1ab27f7750d3056fb68ab355ae1ad","tid":285982,"uid":52269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樣<br />\n以前雄心壯志 雖然無目標 <br />\n但都會相信自己會有翻成就<br />\n望住 身邊人grad job既人工<br />\n我就發現好多野整定<br />\n唔係專科 讀得幾勁都無用<br />\n其實仲有好多例子話你知<br />\n學歷同人工係唔成正比</blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前真係覺得自己點都唔會太差<br />\n而家望到身邊人一個一個搵到份唔錯既工<br />\n先發現之前實在睇得自己太高<br />\n而家慢慢咁接受緊個事實又要再搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d921df1d51ba4e7093c743a453d0e774c9f0085","tid":285982,"uid":87819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企有冇錢 個樣靚唔靚仔冇得改變<br />\n但人生係自己決定的<br />\n<br />\n你覺得自己好廢既 冷靜一下 諗下自己想做咩<br />\n諗到就去做<br />\n想學車 上網申請 想讀書 睇下有冇邊間肯收你<br />\n想去旅行咪去囉<br />\n呢d先係人生<br />\n唔好再花時間諗點解自己咁廢 花多d時間諗下自己有咩想做 再去做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：25歲 OT中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n思想正確!"},{"pid":"d9d9ae5de0b624aa9a0b7b44ae3da9e064c5176e","tid":285982,"uid":113092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲 正面d  每個人都有存在價值 努力去尋找自已既價值"},{"pid":"fdb1d324076f54bd929f595785952f6255e10ab8","tid":285982,"uid":32707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"咁似我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c207c0d33c66d316fc854078f93e2f39e77dbb","tid":285982,"uid":34442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"但係你有個地盤仔男友 濕撚哂都唔驚啦"},{"pid":"f3d24d76f1e3163b7fcd1c4acf16d631c6c2c6d0","tid":285982,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:48:23.000Z","msg":"算啦我25歲都係咁,人生已完"},{"pid":"0d1646ea5013b9ac00107735652ddb7846e93add","tid":285982,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>27歲 做左份工 7年 一無是處 最近老闆減人工 想走但又無其他技能 唉</blockquote><br />\n邊行?"},{"pid":"c10d68057105078ee192d44154d46679c8183f8c","tid":285982,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"暫時目標<br />\n揾到政府文職<br />\n然後一路做<br />\n做到退休老死<br />\n完美人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3aaab8e97c77edde70e347200ec75f2de0f5c6","tid":285982,"uid":47426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:59:12.000Z","msg":"冇目標，依加開始番全職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de14b6a42e4b60c49e134f399d47d1249ccbac8d","tid":285982,"uid":32828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"22歲做緊野，有車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但一樣冇人生目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba89992ad7f6057ad4ff31b59e8da0695edb23eb","tid":285982,"uid":11222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb83e9eb8fd8bd25e68cfded5a8865dc5af6561","tid":285982,"uid":30724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廿二好後生姐</blockquote><br />\n好多22歲人都有車有樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 人之所以痛苦係因為有比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6250152caf774de5bb9f46f5e5f05bc54e9157b9","tid":285982,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n垃圾人生</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb90ffc82486835cccb939aa1a11fbc658ab1b6","tid":285982,"uid":66045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"呢幾個過緊呢種人生<br />\n唯一好少少係有做返運動<br />\n但就窮到賣屎忽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d4eea9b6ec2d019abb52bb1a1e29aff874d916","tid":285982,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"一樣但有車牌 屋企做生意 仲讀緊書 女朋友都有錢"},{"pid":"027fe1a03e4490f7c1edd3febbbce26d1909a2d8","tid":285982,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:13:23.000Z","msg":"可以點算"},{"pid":"a73cee22dfe2023d1d9ff774ce8e1f998e7dff68","tid":285982,"uid":82234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:27:41.000Z","msg":"22時同你一樣 宜家都同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3eeb40924a86fe01cebfc0e1b019b7f502fb58","tid":285982,"uid":52107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:29:27.000Z","msg":"留係屋企hea都唔知